title: Landing Wavedash when you don't have a dodge?! (New trick)

media:group.media:title: Landing Wavedash when you don't have a dodge?! (New trick)
media:group.media:description:
This trick has been hiding in plain sight for at least a year, but nobody is using it. The purpose of this video is to show you how you can do a wavedash when you don't have your dodge and why this is so good that it should be used all the time.
Thanks to Heon_X for graciously providing me with some clips. You can find him on https://twitch.tv/heon_x

Speedometer plugin: https://bakkesplugins.com/plugins/view/73

8:13 The faster way to do it
8:50 Half Flips
